  "detailed_description": "Help Ms. <i>Rabisco</i> to find the moon's lost stars and bring back the light, in this cute but dangerous world, inspired by the <i>World's Hardest Game.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125860/extras/966a226bf5b02b586ea1bacf7234843a.avif?t=1603985198\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Massive world with 100 levels and 300+ screens of precise running and secrets.<br></li><li>Super tight control schemes designed for both keyboards and controllers.<br></li><li>Cute crayon art style with bright colors and hand drawn lines.<br></li><li>Hardcore difficulty 20+ types of enemies and interactable objects.<br></li><li>Lovely soundtrack inspired by Bossa Nova, the famous Brazilian musical genre.</li></ul><br><i>The night was so bright it could be mistaken by the day.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125860/extras/e6a878f87a279b4531ab98882464c685.avif?t=1603985198\" width=600 height=128 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Help Ms. <i>Rabisco</i> to find the moon's lost stars and bring back the light, in this cute but dangerous world, inspired by the <i>World's Hardest Game.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125860/extras/966a226bf5b02b586ea1bacf7234843a.avif?t=1603985198\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Massive world with 100 levels and 300+ screens of precise running and secrets.<br></li><li>Super tight control schemes designed for both keyboards and controllers.<br></li><li>Cute crayon art style with bright colors and hand drawn lines.<br></li><li>Hardcore difficulty 20+ types of enemies and interactable objects.<br></li><li>Lovely soundtrack inspired by Bossa Nova, the famous Brazilian musical genre.</li></ul><br><i>The night was so bright it could be mistaken by the day.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1125860/extras/e6a878f87a279b4531ab98882464c685.avif?t=1603985198\" width=600 height=128 /></span>",
